{"tid":1486341,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《文匯報》A1﹣ 暴徒圖衝中聯辦 警嚴密戒備挫敗","createTime":"2019-08-19T00:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T03:20:03.000Z","uid":49136,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0b4a746387447d326280bde539a0f0d106a2b0","tid":1486341,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:13:51.000Z","msg":"民陣發起的維園黑衣人集會，又演變成造成癱瘓港島北交通的非法遊行，有縱暴黑手在網上號召「去中聯辦打招呼」，流動武器車已在中環集結派「裝備」，探子又到西環踩線。但警方外弛內張，下午已在中聯辦一帶部署嚴密防線，大批便衣探員監察人流走向，並截查可疑人士。暴徒無機可乘及失去掩護，其衝擊中聯辦圖謀被挫敗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNwUnkN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNwUnkN.png&h=ebc06957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">豉油：<br />\n【報章A1速覽】百萬人傘下再聚 「和理非」爭五訴求：全國典範豐富「一國兩制」新實踐<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=359615&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359615%26refer%3DShare&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSstagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=523e68da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359615%26refer%3DShare&h=4c3e59e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=359615&amp;refer=Share</a></span>"},{"pid":"9013f1580f80ae627233aa6270ac30abf393e39f","tid":1486341,"uid":29784,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:15:19.000Z","msg":"柒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4fffb5517915d0e80f6c50c69baebe8fe68c99","tid":1486341,"uid":51790,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:16:10.000Z","msg":"咁都有得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d18